There are four classifications of pronouns available for use in
coding.
   pronoun, possessive, objective, absolute possessive

Darkwind supports single-player, non-archaic male/female/neuter
pronouns.

The queries will return as follows:

query_pronoun()        returns: he, she, it
query_possessive()     returns: his, her, its
query_objective()      returns: him, her, it
query_abs_possessive() returns: his, hers, its

